# ==========================================
# WEBHOOK EVENTS
# ==========================================
#
# PrivyID will send these events to your webhook:
# - sent: Signature request sent to signer
# - delivered: Email delivered to signer
# - opened: Signer opened email
# - viewed: Signer viewed document
# - signed: Document successfully signed
# - declined: Signer declined to sign
# - expired: Signature request expired
#
