# SECURITY NOTES
# ==========================================
#
# 1. NEVER commit this file with real credentials
# 2. Webhook signature verification is REQUIRED
# 3. Store signed documents securely (S3 with encryption)
# 4. Implement rate limiting on webhook endpoint
# 5. Use HTTPS in production
